data.description: HUGE PRICE REDUCTION!  SELLER SAYS, GET THIS SOLD NOW!!    Gentleman farm or horse farm in a beautiful private location on 4.9 acres. Spacious home! Very light and bright! Close to Spokane, a short drive, and you're in the country! Large shop being used as a barn, and additional two car garage connected to home through a breezeway. Lots of room for parking! Round pen that stays. All new faucets in the guest bath. Primary bath has new shower heads. New floors in primary bedroom, den and one of the guest rooms. Playset and trampoline stay! Fenced front yard for your dogs. Room for horses, llamas, sheep, goats, or any animal you like. Fridge and washer/dryer go with seller. Cooling is an evaporative cooling system. This home is a gem!
